OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 05 MAY
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1980FJan Leeming was the duty news
OL,7,Fpresenter on Bank Holiday Monday. News
OL,8,Fbroke that the SAS stormed the Iranian
OL,9,FEmbassy. Jan presented a Newsflash (BBC
OL,10,FTwo), breaking into snooker coverage.
OL,11,FIt was the longest Newsflash ever
OL,12,Fcarried on BBC One/BBC Two. Kate Adie
OL,13,Fwas the main reporter at the scene.
